le=\\\"margin:0in 0in 8pt 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;line-height:17.12px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span>The right to erasure \\u2013 You have the right to request that we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 8pt 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;line-height:17.12px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span>The right to restrict processing \\u2013 You have the right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 8pt 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;line-height:17.12px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span>The right to object to processing \\u2013 You have the right to object to our processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 8pt 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;line-height:17.12px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Symbol;\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span>The right to data portability \\u2013 You have the right to request that we transfer the data and information that we have collected to another organization, or directly to you, under certain conditions.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you would like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.25in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.25in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">9. \\u00a0Security of your Personal Information<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.25in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">a)<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Your account profile is available through a password and unique customer ID selected by you. This password is encrypted.<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">b)<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Your Personal information resides on a secure computer system<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">c)<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Employees and third party partners must sign confidentiality agreements to protect<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Customer and other confidential information<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">d)<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Encrypt credit card information on our order forms using secure socket layer (SSL) technology<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">Members are responsible for any action taken under the name of their accounts. Green Stock shall not be liable for any loss or deletion of the Content.<\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\">No method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. Therefore, while we make <\\/span>best efforts to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraph\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">10. Children<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">Another important priority of ours is adding protection for children while using the internet. We encourage parents and guardians to observe, participate in, and\\/or monitor and guide their online activity.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">GreenStock does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information from children under the age of 13. If you think that your child provided this kind of information on our website, we strongly encourage you to contact us immediately and we will do our best efforts to promptly remove such information from our records.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.25in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><\\/div>\"}', '2021-06-09 08:50:42', '2023-11-25 22:55:36');
