(77, 'policy_pages.element', '{\"title\":\"License\",\"details\":\"<div><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">Last Updated: Nov 2023<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">The following is a legal agreement between you and MS Motion Designs LLC DBA GreenStock, Green Stock (in this agreement referred to as \\u201cGreenStock\\u201d) that explains how you can use photos, illustrations, vectors, video clips and template project files that you license from the Green Stock. By downloading content from Green Stock, you accept this entire agreement.<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\">LICENSES<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);text-indent:-0.25in;\\\">1.<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span>Standard License for\\u00a0 Photos, Vectors and Graphics<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.5in;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);\\\">Every file you download from GreenStock comes with a standard license.\\u00a0 It grants you the right to use the content (images, vectors, graphics and videos) as follows;<\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 0in 0.25in;font-size:12pt;